{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/Fix-Calendar-Display-Of-BlogEngineNET/","result":{"data":{"sitePage":{"id":"SitePage /posts/Fix-Calendar-Display-Of-BlogEngineNET/"}},"pageContext":{"url":"/posts/Fix-Calendar-Display-Of-BlogEngineNET/","relativePath":"posts/Fix-Calendar-Display-Of-BlogEngineNET.md","relativeDir":"posts","base":"Fix-Calendar-Display-Of-BlogEngineNET.md","name":"Fix-Calendar-Display-Of-BlogEngineNET","frontmatter":{"title":"更正BlogEngine.NET的日历显示","stackbit_url_path":"posts/Fix-Calendar-Display-Of-BlogEngineNET","date":"2011-07-26 08:22:00","excerpt":"本文解释了在BlogEngine.NET中，日历部件显示问题的出现原因，以及解决办法。","comments_count":0,"positive_reactions_count":0,"tags":["BlogEngine.NET","Calendar","日历"],"canonical_url":"https://be-net.azurewebsites.net/post/2011/07/26/Fix-Calendar-Display-Of-BlogEngineNET","template":"post"},"html":"<h1><span style=\"color: #800080;\">一、症状：</span></h1>\n<p>BlogEngine.NET 的日历部件，在中文状态下，星期部分显示不全，如下图所示：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/image_39.png\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 240px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 92.56756756756756%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\" src=\"/static/f463565f6de781e81af5b1089f908456/8ff5a/image_thumb_39.png\" srcset=\"/static/f463565f6de781e81af5b1089f908456/12f09/image_thumb_39.png 148w,\n/static/f463565f6de781e81af5b1089f908456/8ff5a/image_thumb_39.png 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></p>\n<h1><span style=\"color: #800080;\">二、原因：</span></h1>\n<p>在此部件的源代码中，对其显示格式作了 DayNameFormat=\"FirstTwoLetters\" 设置，这个设置没有考虑到中文的显示效果。</p>\n<p>当在英文文化环境下时，取前两位字母，显示效果如下：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/image_40.png\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 240px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 89.1891891891892%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\" src=\"/static/d25c11e60cdec445c946401e8c556fd3/8ff5a/image_thumb_40.png\" srcset=\"/static/d25c11e60cdec445c946401e8c556fd3/12f09/image_thumb_40.png 148w,\n/static/d25c11e60cdec445c946401e8c556fd3/8ff5a/image_thumb_40.png 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></p>\n<p>源代码路径：~\\BlogEngine.NET\\widgets\\Calendar\\widget.ascx</p>\n<pre class=\"brush: html\">...\n&lt;blog:PostCalendar ID=\"PostCalendar1\" runat=\"Server\" NextMonthText=\"&gt;&gt;\" DayNameFormat=\"FirstTwoLetters\"\n        FirstDayOfWeek=\"monday\" PrevMonthText=\"&lt;&lt;\" CssClass=\"calendar\" BorderWidth=\"0\"\n        WeekendDayStyle-CssClass=\"weekend\" OtherMonthDayStyle-CssClass=\"other\" UseAccessibleHeader=\"true\"\n        EnableViewState=\"false\" /&gt;\n...</pre>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1><span style=\"color: #800080;\">三、解决方案：</span></h1>\n<p>将上述源代码修改为如下代码后（DayNameFormat=\"Short\" ），即可。</p>\n<p>源代码路径：~\\BlogEngine.NET\\widgets\\Calendar\\widget.ascx</p>\n<pre class=\"brush: html\">...\n&lt;blog:PostCalendar ID=\"PostCalendar1\" runat=\"Server\" NextMonthText=\"&gt;&gt;\" DayNameFormat=\"Short\"\n        FirstDayOfWeek=\"monday\" PrevMonthText=\"&lt;&lt;\" CssClass=\"calendar\" BorderWidth=\"0\"\n        WeekendDayStyle-CssClass=\"weekend\" OtherMonthDayStyle-CssClass=\"other\" UseAccessibleHeader=\"true\"\n        EnableViewState=\"false\" /&gt;\n...</pre>\n<h1><span style=\"color: #800080;\">四、解决后的图示如下：</span></h1>\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"2\" width=\"400\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"200\" valign=\"top\">中文环境</td>\n<td width=\"200\" valign=\"top\">英文环境</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"200\" valign=\"top\"><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/image_41.png\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 240px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 95.94594594594595%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\" src=\"/static/d85b319c56628d0e6df030fd583f3e0e/8ff5a/image_thumb_41.png\" srcset=\"/static/d85b319c56628d0e6df030fd583f3e0e/12f09/image_thumb_41.png 148w,\n/static/d85b319c56628d0e6df030fd583f3e0e/8ff5a/image_thumb_41.png 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></td>\n<td width=\"200\" valign=\"top\"><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/image_42.png\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 240px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 89.86486486486487%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\" src=\"/static/40e41b9402aef2ffc83f9be1b0294077/8ff5a/image_thumb_42.png\" srcset=\"/static/40e41b9402aef2ffc83f9be1b0294077/12f09/image_thumb_42.png 148w,\n/static/40e41b9402aef2ffc83f9be1b0294077/8ff5a/image_thumb_42.png 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>[donate:www.zizhujy.com]</p>","pages":[],"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeff Tian","author":"@zizhujy","description":"A wild full stack developer","palette":"yellow","header":{"title":"Jeff Tian","tagline":"A wild developer","logo_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7z1ua3nTOC5B7DwwzAki8I/4e1a05f8db770c285a492eeb1eaa398f/imageedit_3_2509022194.png","background_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7m0jrKYaDBwEvlc5lo8nt6/6d50a5050d9cdc0d4d2047e35feac292/10648733_696750647079056_2800539603462658695_o.jpg","has_nav":true,"nav_links":[{"label":"Home","url":"/","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"About","url":"/about","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"关于","url":"https://ggyy.pa-pa.me/about","style":"link","icon_class":"lorem-ipsum","new_wind